Sentencas: Ni/NiFe 2 coatings with different thickness of Ni were deposited on 50-h pre -oxidized SUS 430 steel by magnetron sputtering for solid oxide fuel cell (SOFC) interconnects application, which were subsequently exposed to 800 degrees C air for durations of up to 5040 h. Ni/NiFe 2 coating was thermally converted to an oxide structure comprising inner NiO layer and outer NiFe 2 O 4 spinel layer.
Titulo: The performance of NiO/NiFe2O4 coated pre-oxidized SUS 430 interconnect with different NiO thickness for solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: The effects of different NiO diffusion barrier thickness on the oxidation behavior, electrical performance and long-term working stability of NiO/NiFe 2 O 4 coated steel were investigated.
Titulo: The performance of NiO/NiFe2O4 coated pre-oxidized SUS 430 interconnect with different NiO thickness for solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: The chromium vaporization from bare and coated steels was also evaluated at 800 degrees C in air -12
Titulo: The performance of NiO/NiFe2O4 coated pre-oxidized SUS 430 interconnect with different NiO thickness for solid oxide fuel cell
The performance of NiO/NiFe2O4 coated pre-oxidized SUS 430 interconnect with different NiO thickness for solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: Results showed that scale delamination and the spike of area specific resistance (ASR) were achieved for the sample with thicker NiO layer after 2520 h thermal exposure.
Titulo: The performance of NiO/NiFe2O4 coated pre-oxidized SUS 430 interconnect with different NiO thickness for solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: Moreover, NiO gradually migrated outward through the solid-state reaction between NiO and NiFe 2 O 4 spinel and eventually aggregated near the outer surface.
Titulo: The performance of NiO/NiFe2O4 coated pre-oxidized SUS 430 interconnect with different NiO thickness for solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: Breakaway oxidation of the bare steel occurred during the chromium vaporization test and undulating Fe oxide nodules were strewn on the steel surface.
Titulo: The performance of NiO/NiFe2O4 coated pre-oxidized SUS 430 interconnect with different NiO thickness for solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: The chromium vaporization rate was effectively suppressed by the application of NiO/NiFe 2 O 4 coating.
Titulo: The performance of NiO/NiFe2O4 coated pre-oxidized SUS 430 interconnect with different NiO thickness for solid oxide fuel cell
